317, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"score\": 0.999977652742975, \"rank\": 2.222945332914407e-05, \"text\": \"Peru\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\"}, {\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998789661127683, \"rank\": 5.687759387582332e-05, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 24 original signatories\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"Crookston\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"the letter\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several more bishops from around the worldalso gave their nameafter the initial publication.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several more bishops\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the worldalso\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"their nameafter\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"the initial publication\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prelates demand that the IOC \\\"repudiate this blasphemous action and apologize to all people of faith,\\\" warning that the display \\\"threatens people of all faiths and of none, as it opens the door to those with power doing whatever they wish to people they do not like.\\\"\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.493909792805262e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prelates\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"this blasphemous action\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"all people\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"the display\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"all faiths\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter's organizers provided an email address - episcopimundi2022@gmail.com - that other bishops can use to add their names to the document.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The letter's organizers\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"an email address\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"other bishops\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"their names\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"the document\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic opening ceremony in the French capital on July 26 triggered global outrage over scenes that included cavorting drag queens in whatmany decried as a mockeryof the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1915, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9960753024673578, \"rank\": 0.003512481273909006, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\